<solution>
<p><ul><li>4.0002669207406</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={1800}{e}^{{{0.23}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{4517}={1800}{e}^{{{0.23}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{4517}}{{1800}}={e}^{{{0.23}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{\ln{{\left(\frac{{4517}}{{1800}}\right)}}}={0.23}{t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{\ln{{\left(\frac{{4517}}{{1800}}\right)}}}}{{0.23}}={t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{t}={4.0002669207406}</m></p>
</solution>
